{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina features views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout includes a living room with kitchen, bedroom, and children's room. The living room is southeast-facing and offers beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The apartment has an ideal orientation compared to other (west-facing) apartments, as in the summer it does not overheat and is comfortable to live in without the need for air conditioning. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet and underfloor electric heating."}
